{"tid":1631424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請手足聽日俾一日自己冷靜下！","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:29:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:02:54.000Z","uid":154783,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d40ee4d8f00731fb8f70e21e29be27147830c63f","tid":1631424,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:29:19.000Z","msg":"哩幾日有啲過份咗<br />\n抖抖冷靜下<br />\n禮拜日再戰好嗎？<br />\n停一日重整旗鼓 並唔係代表我地屈服<br />\n大丈夫能屈能伸！<br />\n<br />\n警察打死手足 我地都無驚過<br />\n我地殺警 佢地都唔會驚到瀨尿㗎<br />\n暴力只會激起更大嘅仇恨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外附上私人魔法守則畀各位新生參考：<br />\n逃走時掩護        🔥  ✅ <br />\n干擾                   💧  ✅<br />\n路障                   🔥  ✅<br />\n俾狗擔走        👊🏿💧✅<br />\n發洩                   💧  ✅<br />\n核心地標裝修👊🏿💧✅"},{"pid":"376689355f5e37685269bf29f52d00dfc7ca12ac","tid":1631424,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:30:56.000Z","msg":"對店舖:<br />\n記住<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔需要次次硬裝修</span></span></strong><br />\n可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">善用</span><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">蟲系魔法</span></strong></span>同埋<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1823</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對人(影大頭相/非主攻類):<br />\n可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong><br />\n唔係下下爆哂缸先叫成功既<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要贏一定要剛柔並用</span>"},{"pid":"6506447e5e2683f56639bb08ea1daefa2ec9ece5","tid":1631424,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:31:21.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n搵返六七月有原則嘅自己啊！"},{"pid":"a06a303110cd9ed09460757056f577937295fbfd","tid":1631424,"uid":75959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:32:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"3fe4608098c8871306b2aef12c0f808d333d7a9b","tid":1631424,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:32:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"668c114b96c4e3fc222987f9c8c476df62432204","tid":1631424,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"376689355f5e37685269bf29f52d00dfc7ca12ac","tid":1631424,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:30:56.000Z","msg":"對店舖:<br />\n記住<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔需要次次硬裝修</span></span></strong><br />\n可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">善用</span><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">蟲系魔法</span></strong></span>同埋<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1823</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對人(影大頭相/非主攻類):<br />\n可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong><br />\n唔係下下爆哂缸先叫成功既<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要贏一定要剛柔並用</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:34:09.000Z","msg":"提議<br />\n男嘅可以除佢衫 用大字寫佢衰乜<br />\n再搵架手推車帶佢散下步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n女既就... 寫喺塊面到？？"},{"pid":"33b30721d301e35096ac8181afd3a640b50f8769","tid":1631424,"uid":63792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:35:16.000Z","msg":"唔好亂裝修呀各位...<br />\n不過唔排除有狗扮手足嫁禍"},{"pid":"84d19d7cd4c1a7ae8e4fb9bc334345779e9b2a76","tid":1631424,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:35:31.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n攬炒經濟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人人自危 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6321fd4ca2796c4d8d7658781d3eefe11e2fa12","tid":1631424,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:37:23.000Z","msg":"【地方的手足需要進化】麻煩大家入黎溫下書，睇下烏克蘭係E個時候做左D咩<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631278\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631278</a>"},{"pid":"17f3ef5616cfe5b23cb3e356fa34d65d7e67575c","tid":1631424,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33b30721d301e35096ac8181afd3a640b50f8769","tid":1631424,"uid":63792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:35:16.000Z","msg":"唔好亂裝修呀各位...<br />\n不過唔排除有狗扮手足嫁禍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:38:46.000Z","msg":"唔使捉鬼 手尾做得好睇就得<br />\n唔使覺得虛偽 錯就要認 俠客風骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n若果附近手足睇唔過眼一定要出聲<br />\n和勇互相制衡 先會走向好結果<br />\n同理三權分立"},{"pid":"b30fbd9c26c5b8329dedb872151526521e139922","tid":1631424,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6321fd4ca2796c4d8d7658781d3eefe11e2fa12","tid":163